  "short_reason": "This is an excellent architectural photograph, using a strong foreground arch to frame the scene and dramatic lighting to create depth and mood.",
  "detailed_reason": "The composition is very effective, with the large, dark arch in the foreground acting as a natural frame that draws the viewer's eye into the grand space of the cathedral. The lighting is a key feature, with warm, golden light highlighting the vaulted ceilings and the repeating lines of the columns, creating a beautiful contrast with the deep shadows. This interplay of light and shadow not only adds a sense of drama and reverence but also emphasizes the immense scale and intricate details of the Gothic architecture.",
  "comparison_reason": null
}

